data.description: Seize the opportunity to own this well-maintained single-family home, ready for its next owner. This inviting property features 3 bedrooms, 1 full bathroom, and a convenient 1-car detached garage. The spacious kitchen seamlessly connects to the dining room and living room, creating a comfortable living space. Enjoy the benefits of a full basement and a walk-up attic for additional storage. Ideally located near Hazard Ave and Enfield Mall, the home provides easy access to a plethora of shopping and dining options. Situated just one street over from Enfield Public Library and Eli Whitney Elementary School, convenience is at your doorstep. With plenty of off-street parking and a 1-car detached garage, this property offers practicality. The large partially fenced yard ensures both privacy and abundant space for family entertainment and fun. Don't miss out on the chance to make this inviting property your new home!
